<br>
Let the wizzie quadkite. You run along the path and either<br>
A ) stand in the path of the runners and pbaoe nuke them<br>
or <br>
B ) use your rains to help with quad. The mobs are close and with 4 targets you get the max out of your rain right after cast.<br>
<br>
